# --- Large Raw Data Files ---
# Zillow national files can be very large; keep them local only.
# Anyone cloning the repo can re-download from zillow.com/research/data/
# Uncomment the lines below if your Zillow CSVs exceed 50MB:
# Data/Raw/Zillow/*.csv

